## Prototype Output Checklist

Before presenting any prototype, verify:

- [ ] All colors use `var(--token-name)` — no hex literals
- [ ] All spacing uses `var(--space-N)` — no px literals
- [ ] Loading, error, empty, and success states all present
- [ ] Mock data is realistic, not placeholder
- [ ] Phone frame wrapper applied with correct dimensions
- [ ] All interactive elements meet 44px touch target minimum
- [ ] Font substitution noted (e.g., "DM Sans used in place of [PRIMARY FONT]")
- [ ] Which design system components are represented — noted at bottom of file

